<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,409,1454,1480]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="286">External morphology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="21.[160,1156,1454,1618]" pageId="21" pageNumber="286">Body elongate, narrow, background colour transparent white. Rhinophores and oral tentacles smooth, translucent with white spots. Cerata smooth, background colour white or beige, base with a green iridescent sphere at their base; first and second row of cerata connected with a dark line.</paragraph>
